CustomField.description: The number of days that will be queried at a time while calling the Engagio API. For example, setting this value to 1 will bring only 1 day at a time while setting to 365 will attempt to bring back one year.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The number of days that will be queried at a time while calling the Engagio API. For example, setting this value to 1 will bring only 1 day at a time while setting to 365 will attempt to bring back one year.
CustomField.label: Engagio API Fetch Days
